author: Nexcell Pride
text:
As always, Rushia has a nice skills at cooking... :_ちょうちょ:
- First were these two deliveries about breakfast (Morning stream)
- Later, Halloween cooking event, with these delicious pancakes...
- And there... These Chocolate biscuit muffins.

The best parts were the "acting endings"... :_きゅん:
Well... Definitively It's the charming of Yasuyuki-sensei's girls, but more especially Rushia... These red eyes with these butterfly shines and these straight eyelashes captivate a lot. :_ハート: :_るんるん:
